    {
      "Case Number": "PES04286101",
      "Case Title": "THE ESTATE OF ESTELLE MACKOTA",
      "Court Date": "2006-04-12 09:00 AM",
      "Examiner": "E. ESTACIO",
      "Calendar Matter": "Notice Of Motion To Compel Richard Mackota To Answer Special Interrogatories & For Sanctions",
      "Rulings": "Matter on Calendar for April 12, 2006. (1) Petitioner Fred Mackota's Motion To Compel Richard Mackota To Answer Special Interrogatories, Set One, is granted as to Nos. 7 and 10. The objections are overruled. The motion is granted as to Nos. 1, 18, 19, and 24. The responses are inadequate and incomplete. The objections are overruled. The motion is denied as to Nos. 33, 34, and 35. The objections are sustained. Sanctions are denied. (2) Petitioner Fred Mackota's Motion To Compel Richard Mackota To Answer Form Interrogatories, Set Two, is granted as to Form Interrogatory Nos. 12.1-12.7. Respondent is ordered to respond further within 10 days of notice of this order. Respondent's responses and opposition were a misuse of the discovery process. Petitioner's request for sanctions is granted in the amount of $515, to be paid within 30 days of notice of this order. = (612/HEWLETT)",
      "Judge": "E. Estacio"
    },
